sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant StreamlitApp as UI (app.py)
    participant JoJoStateMachine as State Machine
    participant ConfigLoadState
    participant UiInitState
    participant IndustryProcessState
    participant DataFetchState
    participant DataHandlerModule as Data Handler
    participant ValuationState
    participant FilteringState
    participant ResultsDisplayState
    participant ExportState

    User->>StreamlitApp: Interacts (e.g., selects industry, clicks button)
    StreamlitApp->>JoJoStateMachine: Updates context, drives state transition
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>ConfigLoadState: execute()
    ConfigLoadState->>DataHandlerModule: (reads industries.json, .env)
    DataHandlerModule-->>ConfigLoadState: config data (implicitly via context)
    ConfigLoadState-->>JoJoStateMachine: next_state = UI_INIT
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>UiInitState: execute() (renders UI, waits for input)
    UiInitState-->>JoJoStateMachine: next_state = UI_INIT (or INDUSTRY_PROCESS on button click)

    Note over StreamlitApp, JoJoStateMachine: On "Start Filter" click
    StreamlitApp->>JoJoStateMachine: context.user_clicked_filter_button = True
    JoJoStateMachine->>UiInitState: execute()
    UiInitState-->>JoJoStateMachine: next_state = INDUSTRY_PROCESS
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>IndustryProcessState: execute()
    IndustryProcessState-->>JoJoStateMachine: next_state = DATA_FETCH
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>DataFetchState: execute()
    DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: get_all_companies_basic_data()
    DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: (updates context.all_companies_openapi_data)
    DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: filter_industry_stocks()
    DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: (updates context.industry_stocks_details)
    loop For each stock_detail in context.industry_stocks_details (limited by limit_stocks)
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: fetch_finmind_financial_statement_data(stock_code, date, "BalanceSheet")
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: df_bs
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: extract_finmind_items(df_bs, bs_items_map)
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: (updates financial_data_for_stock)
        
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: fetch_finmind_financial_statement_data(stock_code, date, "CashFlowsStatement")
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: df_cf
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: extract_finmind_items(df_cf, cf_items_map)
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: (updates financial_data_for_stock with capex, depreciation)
        
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: fetch_finmind_financial_statement_data(stock_code, date, "FinancialStatements")
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: df_is
        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: extract_finmind_items(df_is, is_items_map)
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: (updates financial_data_for_stock with net_income, eps)

        DataFetchState->>DataHandlerModule: fetch_finmind_stock_price(stock_code, target_date)
        DataHandlerModule-->>DataFetchState: current_market_price
    end
    DataFetchState-->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(VALUATION)
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>ValuationState: execute()
    loop For each stock_code, financials in context.processed_data
        ValuationState->>DataHandlerModule: calculate_dcf_valuation(stock_code, financials, risk, context)
        DataHandlerModule-->>ValuationState: valuation_result (appended to context.valuation_results)
    end
    ValuationState-->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(FILTERING)
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>FilteringState: execute() (filters context.valuation_results into context.filtered_results, adds warnings if needed)
    FilteringState-->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(RESULTS_DISPLAY)
    
    JoJoStateMachine->>ResultsDisplayState: execute() (renders results table in UI using context.filtered_results)
    Note right of ResultsDisplayState: Stays in RESULTS_DISPLAY until UI interaction.

    Note over StreamlitApp, JoJoStateMachine: On "重新查詢" (New Query) click in Results UI
    StreamlitApp->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(UI_INIT)

    Note over StreamlitApp, JoJoStateMachine: On "匯出結果" (Export) click in Results UI (if implemented)
    StreamlitApp->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(EXPORT)

    JoJoStateMachine->>ExportState: execute() (TODO: implement export logic)
    ExportState-->>JoJoStateMachine: transition_to(RESULTS_DISPLAY) # Or UI_INIT
